---
source: crates/opencode-cli/tests/cli_help_snapshots.rs
expression: "render_help(&[\"opencode\", \"prompt\", \"--help\"])"
---
Run a single one-shot prompt and exit

Usage: opencode prompt [OPTIONS] <TEXT>

Arguments:
  <TEXT>  The prompt text

Options:
      --output <OUTPUT>          Output format: text | json [default: text]
      --timeout-ms <TIMEOUT_MS>  Timeout budget for backend request acceptance in milliseconds [default: 30000]
  -h, --help                     Print help
